{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"And olsun günəşə və onun saçdığı şəfəqə!","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-shamsi waḍuḥāhā ","translations":["By the sun","and its brightness","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-shamsi","waḍuḥāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,2575]]}},{"name":"91:2","price":"And olsun onu təqib edən aya!","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-qamari idhā talāhā ","translations":["And the moon","when","it follows it","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-qamari","idhā","talāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1630],[3,1630,3095]]}},{"name":"91:3","price":"And olsun (günəşi) parlaq edən gündüzə!","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-nahāri idhā jallāhā ","translations":["And the day","when","it displays it","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-nahāri","idhā","jallāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2240],[2,2240,2870],[3,2870,4345]]}},{"name":"91:4","price":"And olsun (günəşi) örtüb-bürüyən gecəyə!","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā yaghshāhā ","translations":["And the night","when","it covers it","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","yaghshāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,1750],[3,1750,3315]]}},{"name":"91:5","price":"And olsun göyə və onu bina edənə! (Yaxud: And olsun göyə və onun yaradılışına).","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahN