:"qad aflaḥa man zakkāhā ","translations":["Indeed","he succeeds","who","purifies it","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["qad","aflaḥa","man","zakkāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1280],[3,1280,2220],[4,2220,3705]]}},{"name":"91:10","price":"Onu (günaha) batıran isə ziyana uğramışdır.","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"waqad khāba man dassāhā ","translations":["And indeed","he fails","who","buries it","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waqad","khāba","man","dassāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1290],[3,1290,2330],[4,2330,3835]]}},{"name":"91:11","price":"Səmud (qövmü) öz azğınlığı üzündən (Allahın elçisi Salehi) inkar etdi.","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"kadhabat thamūdu biṭaghwāhā ","translations":["Denied","Thamud","by their transgression","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kadhabat","thamūdu","biṭaghwāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,1920],[3,1920,3585]]}},{"name":"91:12","price":"Onların ən bədbəxti (dəvəni kəsməyə) qalxdığı zaman","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"az","meta":{"transliteration":"idhi inbaʿatha ashqāhā ","translations":["When","(was) sent forth","(the) most wicked of them","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["idhi","inbaʿatha","ashqāhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1970],[3,1970,3365]]}},{"name":"91:13","price":"Allahın elçisi (Saleh) onlara: “Allahın (bu) dişi dəvəsinə toxunmayın və onun su içməsinə mane olmayın!”– dedi.","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","la